text: Kenny Ewell Marchant (born February 23, 1951) is an American politician. He was the U.S. representative for , from 2005 to 2021. He was a member of the Republican Party. On August 5, 2019, Marchant announced that he would not seek re-election in 2020. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from Texas Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Members of the Texas Legislature
